# .mailmap file maps author/committer names and emails
# This allows GitHub to correctly group contributors without rewriting history
# Format: Proper Name <proper@email.com> <old@email.com>
# Format: Proper Name <proper@email.com> Old Name <old@email.com>
# Format: Proper Name <proper@email.com> Old Name <old@email.com> Old Name2 <old2@email.com>

# Main account - all commits should be attributed to this
